name: Rewind Me Cassette T-Shirt
description: We've seen a lot of shirts with the whole Cassette w/crossbones theme. But instead of just switching out the skull with a cassette, why not also swap the crossbones for something that actually has to do with the owning of a cassette?! We tried our best to still make it look badass.

name: Happy King Kong T-Shirt
description:
This design is a whimsical re-imagination of the classic King Kong scene. We depicted the giant gorilla as more of a blue yeti monster (who apparently has quite the odd affection for the Empire State Building)... because we just really love monsters. 

Available on : White Crewneck, V-Neck.

name: I Heart Vinyl T-Shirt
description:
Dedicated to the love of physical media with high quality lossless sound, a perfect shirt for anyone who collects or enjoys vinyl. 

Available on : White Crewneck, V-Neck.

name: I Heart Coffee Squirrel T-Shirt
description:
For some reason, squirrels have often appeared in media to represent the exaggerated effects of caffeine. We don't really know if squirrels actually like coffee... but this cartoon one sure does!

Available on : White Crewneck, V-Neck.

name: Media Scoop T-Shirt
description:
It's a scoop of ice cream. Wait, no... it's little scoops of TV served up in tasty waffle cones! Deliciously Entertaining. 

Available on : White Crewneck, V-Neck.

name: DrumHead Skull T-Shirt
description:
What do you get when you combine the badassery of a skull and crossbones design with a snare and some drum sticks? This!

Available on : White Crewneck, V-Neck.

name: Metal Hippie T-shirt
description:
This is a kaleidoscopic collage of different color ink illustrations. If you look closely, you'll notice branches, leaves, and wood grain in the pattern. Want in on a little secret? The main source for this design was the illustration art used for another one of our shirts in a different category! The two look nothing alike, but give yourself a pat on the back if you figure it out! 

Available on : White Crewneck, V-Neck.

name: Tapestree T-Shirt
description:
It's a tree that grows cassettes instead of leaves?! Preposterous!!

This illustration came from a concept to create a classic nature scene (a tree on top of a hill) with a strong musical theme. Not only is the tree itself entangled in audio cables, and covered in multicolor cassette leaves, but the shape of the tree itself was made to resemble a cassette. The design was drawn by hand onto a textured fabric to give it a distinct look. 

Available on : White Crewneck, V-Neck.

name: Ravin' Raven T-Shirt
description: Part of an ongoing series of animals made up of colorful geometric mosaic patterns, Ravin' Raven was originally created to be a trippy animated gif image. We only wish we could make this bird actually look like this on the shirt: Available on : White Crewneck.

name: Cassette Owls T-Shirt
description:
This illustration came from a pretty basic concept. Cassettes sort of resemble the head of an owl... at least in a cartoonish kind of way. If you didn't notice that before, we're sure you do now!
One of our most popular designs!

Available on : White Crewneck, V-Neck.
